<h1>Articles!</h1>

This Blog has <%= Article.public_count %> public articles and counting!!!
This Blog has <%= Article.private_count %> private articles and counting!!!
This Blog has <%= Article.archived_count %> archived articles and counting!!!

<ul>
    <% @articles.each do |article| %>
        <% unless article.archived? %>
            <li>
                <%= link_to article.title, article %>
            </li>
        <% end %>
    <% end %>
</ul>

<%= link_to "New Article", new_article_path %>

